      "versionNonce": 266012340,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774868608823,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Means in one class there are going to be methods liek PaywithUPI, payWithCreditCard, etc so for each such algo\ncreate a classes, means add one layer of abstractiona and use it out class and implement this methods in \nsaparate classes called creditCardPaymentStrategy, UPIPaymentStrategy Like this...",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
